DBIx-PgLink version 0.01
========================

NAME
    DBIx::PgLink - external database access from PostgreSQL backend using
    Perl DBI

DESCRIPTION
    *PgLink* is based on *DBI-Link* project for accessing external data
    sources from PostgreSQL backend.

    This module can be used only in untrusted PL/Perl function.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

     perl Makefile.PL
     make
     make install

or

     perl Build.PL
     ./Build
     ./Build install

Testing of module requires extra setup of PostgreSQL database and environment,
described in <Install.html>


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Moose
  MooseX::Method
  DBI
  DBD::xxx (for your database)
  Tie::Cache::LRU


